snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Jammalamadugu || Something Missamma || Episode 03 || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Jammalamadugu Something Missamma Episode 03 MCM

Filmymoji releases its third episode of something Missamma series where on one hand Middle class Madhu reaches Rayalaseema in the lorry he has fallen into and on the other hand Naatu Guntala Gang along with their fathers would be blaming 1A master for taking them to a fake Anjanam practitioner. Inspite of not helping them to find Madhu, Police warn the media people not to put any Ads regarding the missing Madhu case. Failing to publish newspaper Ad, they decide to spread the news through WhatsApp. When they reveal the news to Madhu‚Äôs mother she gets really worried and emotional and urges everyone to find and get back her son asap. Madhu gets down from the lorry when it stopped to unload the flower baskets at a marriage function. Madhu meets an opportunist by the name BuggaReddy, who after knowing Madhu‚Äôs story leaves him with a suggest to gel along with the marriage party to survive. Madhu gets a lot of chores from a lady called Aandaalu. Suddenly Madhu hears some female‚Äôs crying voice. Watch the full episode to find out who the female crying was and would Madhu figures out a way to get away from Rayalaseema.

localized.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Jammalamadugu Something Missamma Episode 03 MCM

Filmymoji releases its third episode of something Missamma series where on one hand Middle class Madhu reaches Rayalaseema in the lorry he has fallen into and on the other hand Naatu Guntala Gang along with their fathers would be blaming 1A master for taking them to a fake Anjanam practitioner. Inspite of not helping them to find Madhu, Police warn the media people not to put any Ads regarding the missing Madhu case. Failing to publish newspaper Ad, they decide to spread the news through WhatsApp. When they reveal the news to Madhu‚Äôs mother she gets really worried and emotional and urges everyone to find and get back her son asap. Madhu gets down from the lorry when it stopped to unload the flower baskets at a marriage function. Madhu meets an opportunist by the name BuggaReddy, who after knowing Madhu‚Äôs story leaves him with a suggest to gel along with the marriage party to survive. Madhu gets a lot of chores from a lady called Aandaalu. Suddenly Madhu hears some female‚Äôs crying voice. Watch the full episode to find out who the female crying was and would Madhu figures out a way to get away from Rayalaseema.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

A young girl named Kaanchi is named a suspect in the murder of two of her family members. Kaanchi is a sweet, seemingly innocent girl who claims to want love and affection from her elders and says she receives hate from them instead. 

Show Name: CID
Show Cast & Characters: 
‚Ä¢ Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
‚Ä¢ Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
‚Ä¢ Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
‚Ä¢ Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
‚Ä¢ Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
‚Ä¢ Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
‚Ä¢ Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
‚Ä¢ Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1289
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #‡§∏‡•Ä‡§Ü‡§à‡§°‡•Ä #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #LIVCrime #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #latestcid 

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: Marvel Studios' The Marvels | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
This fall, The Marvels take flight.

Carol Danvers aka Captain Marvel has reclaimed her identity from the tyrannical Kree and taken revenge on the Supreme Intelligence. But unintended consequences see Carol shouldering the burden of a destabilized universe. When her duties send her to an anomalous wormhole linked to a Kree revolutionary, her powers become entangled with that of Jersey City super-fan, Kamala Khan aka Ms. Marvel, and Carol's estranged niece, now S.A.B.E.R. astronaut Captain Monica Rambeau. Together, this unlikely trio must team-up and learn to work in concert to save the universe as "The Marvels."

Marvel Studios' "The Marvels" stars Brie Larson, Teyonah Parris, Iman Vellani, Zawe Ashton, Gary Lewis, Park Seo-joon, Zenobia Shroff, Mohan Kapur, Saagar Shaikh, and Samuel L. Jackson.

Nia DaCosta directs with Kevin Feige producing. Louis D'Esposito, Victoria Alonso, Mary Livanos, Jonathan Schwartz and Matthew Jenkins serve as executive producers. The screenplay is by Megan McDonnell, Nia DaCosta, Elissa Karasik and Zeb Wells.

Dhokala Recipe -  
 ‚Ä¢ Take oil, sugar Powder, citric Acid, hing, turmeric Powder and water into a mixer jar. Grind all the ingredients well. 
 ‚Ä¢ Add besan and water then again churn it for some time. 
 ‚Ä¢ Then grease a tray with little oil & Put some water for boiling into a steamer.
 ‚Ä¢ Once water is boling add baking soda to the besan mixture & churn the batter for 5-10 Seconds. 
 ‚Ä¢ Then Pour this batter into the greased tray.
 ‚Ä¢ Put this tray into a steamer and steam for 15 to 20 minutes. 
 ‚Ä¢ After 15 to 20 minutes, check if the dhokala is ready using toothpick. 
 ‚Ä¢ If toothpick comes out clean, it indicates dhokala is cooked completely
 ‚Ä¢ Take the dhokala out and allow it to cool down completely. 
 ‚Ä¢ For Tadka, Take a small pan, add oil, mustard, curry leaves, green chillies, sesame for tadka add water, salt and sugar and boil for 2-3 minutes.
 ‚Ä¢ Cut the dhokla into small pieces & Add the tadka water on top of the ready dhokala . Garnish this with Chopped Fresh coriander.

Dhokala Recipe -  
 ‚Ä¢ Take oil, sugar Powder, citric Acid, hing, turmeric Powder and water into a mixer jar. Grind all the ingredients well. 
 ‚Ä¢ Add besan and water then again churn it for some time. 
 ‚Ä¢ Then grease a tray with little oil & Put some water for boiling into a steamer.
 ‚Ä¢ Once water is boling add baking soda to the besan mixture & churn the batter for 5-10 Seconds. 
 ‚Ä¢ Then Pour this batter into the greased tray.
 ‚Ä¢ Put this tray into a steamer and steam for 15 to 20 minutes. 
 ‚Ä¢ After 15 to 20 minutes, check if the dhokala is ready using toothpick. 
 ‚Ä¢ If toothpick comes out clean, it indicates dhokala is cooked completely
 ‚Ä¢ Take the dhokala out and allow it to cool down completely. 
 ‚Ä¢ For Tadka, Take a small pan, add oil, mustard, curry leaves, green chillies, sesame for tadka add water, salt and sugar and boil for 2-3 minutes.
 ‚Ä¢ Cut the dhokla into small pieces & Add the tadka water on top of the ready dhokala . Garnish this with Chopped Fresh coriander.

Poovithal thumbalennil snehamennezhuthi ni
Poomaripolennulil niraye niraye pozhiyunne...
Ramazha chandham neeye ragamay peyyuneee...
Raakaatineenam niyen manavum thanavum nirayunne...
Nenjoramake chayukilee
Nenjudukin thalamay..
kannoramenum theedi nine kankal chimmum neravum.
Eetho niyokam pole iravum pakalum theliyunne...
Niyilla yenkil udalil urukum thiriyonulayunne
(Poovithal...)

Imakal moodum neram mizhi vaathil nii Theliye...
Dhinavum thedunarikee
Pranayam pol neerunne...
Ninavil nirayum nizhale
mazhanoolazhakin oliye...
Ini ee janmam muzhuvan thunnayay nii thudarenam
madhuravasadham nirayum paatin pallavi niyallee..
Pranayasugandham nurayum malaril shalabam njanale..
Nii ragam puthu ragam shruthi cheraamivide...
Nii megam Mazha megam manadharin varamee..
En manasavedhiyiloru nadanathil azhakathu neeyalle.
(Poovithal)


Akamee nirayum puzhanii.. Akathaaril ni ozhukee...
Urukum manamonnivde mazha choodum maruvaay...
Tharalam hridhayam thiraye..thanuvil thazhukum thanu nii..
Pranayam pakarum pen poovonnivide vidarunne..
Anudhinamarikil nira nilavayen innayay neeyileel..
hridhayamudangi ravin madiyil poliyum tharam njan.
Nii thaalam thudi thaalam idanenjin shruthiyee...
Nii moham mazha moham peythozhiyathakame...
Premarthramorathma vipakgika meetamirumey cherumbol { poovithal }

Jiwe jatt ni Jiwe jatt ni

Ove rakhe kehda gudiya to fasla
Ove kehda kare vairi naa mukabla
Ove jachda ae kihde rang sanwla
Ove kehda billo shak ke ni tola awe

Ove kihda dhup wangu luck khide 
Ni kihda aa batinde ale warga
Batheri turi dharti te khach fire
Anti bade anti dot jatt da 
kite hai ni kite hai ni
Ove kehda janda jada vich beh ni 
Jiwe main ni jiwe main ni
Ove kehda enna khara dekh lai ni
Jiwe main ni jiwe main ni

Ove elbow tayi kihne kaff mode billo
Ove kihne off roading te balliye 
Gaddiyan te gaddiyan de tyre tode billo 
Ni ove kehda teer angu sidha awe
Ni ghoda laike teri gutt jidda awe
Ni jithe khade khaddiyan creezan ala 
Ni othe billo harr velly giddha paawe
Bahute yaar sade and ne goriye 
Thode bahar ni thode bahar ni 
Ove kehda rehnda tyaar bar tyaar ni 
Jime yaar ni jime yaar ni
Ove kehda rakhe jutti jhaad jhaad ni 
Jime yaar ni jime yaar ni

snippet.description:

Episode 3829: Bazigar Iyer
--------------------------------------------------------
While everyone waits for Iyer to arrive and deliver the good news, Jethalal is worried about losing. Tapu Sena and other members of the society stand to welcome the good news and watch the bet of Jetha and Iyer. Anjali arrives in the society and everyone starts dancing as they thought that Babita and Iyer have brought their car. Champaklal finds out later about Jethalal and Iyer's wager and asks Jetha to enjoy the wager. Who will win this wager? Continue watching to find out what happens next!

Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Part 3 of 9 - Kena Upanishad - By Sandeep Maheshwari | Spirituality Session Hindi
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com
Connect with him at Facebook.com/SandeepMaheshwariPage
Watch his inspirational videos at Youtube.com/SandeepSeminars
Watch his videos on spirituality at Youtube.com/SandeepMaheshwariSpirituality

When the media mistakenly links the two, Serkan plans to use Eda to get his ex-girlfriend back who had left him and got engaged to another man. The unlikely pair come to an agreement. Eda will pretend to be Serkan‚Äôs fianc√©e, and he will restore her scholarship in return. The arrangement will only last for a couple of months until his ex‚Äôs wedding but pretending to be the fianc√©e of Istanbul‚Äôs most eligible bachelor turns out to be a lot harder than Eda has imagined.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3828 | 20 July 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3828: Jethalal Bribes Goli
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak and Jetha try to design a strategy to learn about Iyer's surprise, but they are unsuccessful. Goli later shows over at Taarak's residence to deliver some snacks baked by his mother. Jetha and Taarak include Goli in their plan to find Iyer's surprise this time. Goli arrives at Iyer's house and inquires about the surprise, but Iyer is skeptical of his motivations. Iyer discovers that Jetha has been listening in on their chat via Goli's phone. Jetha and Taarak's scheme fails once more, and they are dissatisfied. Will Jetha fail the challenge and surrender to Iyer? Continue watching to find out what happens next!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3828, 20 July 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. snippet.title: Lo Aayi Barsaat Official Video | Darshan Raval | Youngveer | Lijo George | Dhruwal Patel | Dard
snippet.description:
Indulge in the magical allure of rainfall as Darshan Raval unleashes a musical storm with his second song from the album Dard, titled 'Lo Aayi Barsaat.' Prepare to be captivated as you immerse yourself in the enchanting melody and rhythmic beats that will surely set your heart on fire. The song is sung and composed by Darshan Raval, while the lyrics are penned by Youngveer. Joining them is Lijo George with his captivating musical beats. This sensational track encapsulates the essence of embracing the drizzle, evoking emotions of joy, love, and longing.

snippet.title: Kuki-Zomi Women Lash Out At Government Over Manipur Assault Video
snippet.description:
People from Kuki-Zomi community gathered at Delhi's Jantar Mantar to protest against the atrocities inflicted on Manipur women after the Manipur assault video, where two Kuki-Zomi women were seen paraded naked and assaulted by a mob of men, went viral. This is what women from Kuki-Zomi community told The Indian Express.

snippet.title: FRIED CHICKEN DRUMSTICK | Chicken Fry Recipe with Mashed Potato | Chicken Recipe Cooking In Village
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook crispy chicken fry recipe using chicken meat and potatoes. We mash the potatoes and chicken then we mix them to make the chicken drumstick recipe. Finally, we fried the chicken in Traditional Gingelly oil.

The taste is crispy!

localized.description:
PRK Productions Presents
"Aachar & Co."
Authentic Taste of Bangalore Since 1971

A delightful blend of nostalgia, humor & drama. It is a coming-of-age story of the siblings of a typical orthodox family as they explore the changes in patriarchy, arranged marriages, gender roles and education and work opportunities for women through the 1960s-70s of Bangalore.

Experience in Cinemas on 28th of July 2023.
